<br>
The basic template I use is at www.auctionsubmit.com. You can just download it once and then enter in all your regular information. Like the types of payments you accept, auction terms, etc.<br>
I have a few graphics I use in my listings but not too many.<br>
You want your auction to load smoothly so that people on any connection can view it quickly and easily. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
